      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"4. POWER VALLEY goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from five starts. In the money last time at this track (20.13) in a Mix, finishing a one length second. Looks a key chance on best form. 1. ROBELL SETH recorded his best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 2.25 lengths second behind Full Twist in 20.32. Looks a leading chance again. 2. TYKETTO turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Most Determined (20.43) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has never been out of the placings from three starts out of this box. Bold showing expected. 3. AUSSIE MAC must be respected at his pet distance.\",\"runners\":[4,1,2,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
